SPARTA README:

Along with this README, the SPARTA team has submitted a compressed directory named SPARTA_VM. This directory contains a VirtualBox installation of Ubuntu with a build of SPARTA and examples using SPARTA.  It also includes all code and dependencies needed to build SPARTA.  Important directories and files and their basic use are outlined here but please consult ~/sparta-code/docs/manual.pdf for in depth instructions.

